     a slider for a simplier and faster input
     defaul 2 as number of file
     the config file (ENV:mvmaster)
     better suffix for subfiles.

     Anyway I've included the source.
     It requires:
     AmosPro 2
     Gui Extension
     Jd extension
     Amcaf extension
     Ldos extension
     
     Have fun!
@endnode
